titles.title: A resolution honoring the 30th anniversary of the partnership between the State of Nebraska and the Czech Republic under the State Partnership Program.
A resolution honoring the 30th anniversary of the partnership between the State of Nebraska and the Czech Republic under the State Partnership Program.

action.text: Referred to the Committee on Foreign Relations.

bill.summary: This resolution expresses continued support for the State Partnership Program between Nebraska and Czechia. The resolution also expresses appreciation for the commitment of Czech armed forces and the Nebraska National Guard in advancing peace, stability and mutual understanding.
